OL,3,C'You never heal' ` families still
OL,4,Cgrieving decades after Glasgow murders
OL,6,FThe sister of a 21-year-old woman who
OL,7,Fwas murdered in Glasgow nearly 30
OL,8,Fyears ago has said she will never get
OL,9,Fover her death, saying "it's your
OL,10,Fsister and you never heal".
OL,12,FBernadette McCash was just 12 when her
OL,13,Fsister Tracey Wylde was choked to
OL,14,Fdeath at her flat in Barmulloch in
OL,15,FNovember 1997.
OL,17,FIt took more than 20 years for her
OL,18,Fkiller, Zhi Min Chen, to be brought to
OL,19,Fjustice.
OL,26,@qD@XOUrD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
