OL,3,C'You never heal' ` families still
OL,4,Cgrieving decades after Glasgow murders
OL,6,FMs Wylde was one of a number of a
OL,7,Fwomen involved in prostitution who
OL,8,Fwere killed in Glasgow the 1990s and
OL,9,Fearly 2000s, whose deaths are being
OL,10,Fexamined by a new podcast.
OL,12,FMs McCash told Rayo's Beware Book
OL,13,Fpodcast that when police came to her
OL,14,Fdoor to say her sister had been
OL,15,Fmurdered, "I was 12 but it never hit
OL,16,Fme".
OL,18,FShe went on: "The school kept me
OL,19,Finside because the paparazzi were
OL,20,Ftrying to pull me out of school.
OL,26,@wD@KOUxD@CO]zD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774832614
OL,3,C'You never heal' ` families still
OL,4,Cgrieving decades after Glasgow murders
OL,6,F"All my friends rallied around me and
OL,7,Fthey were asking if that was my sister
OL,8,Fin the paper and on TV.
OL,10,F"You never heal, it's your sister and
OL,11,Fyou never heal.
OL,13,F"Twenty odd years down the line, you
OL,14,Fjust learn to cope but the heartache
OL,15,Fis still there."
OL,17,FThe podcast also spoke to Alice
OL,18,FWilson, whose daughter Jacqueline
OL,19,FGallagher was brutally murdered in
OL,20,FJune 1996.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@AOUwD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
