OL,3,C'You never heal' ` families still
OL,4,Cgrieving decades after Glasgow murders
OL,6,FMs Wilson said her daughter had been
OL,7,F"a lovely lassie, beautiful looking".
OL,9,F"She was born with jet black hair, it
OL,10,Fwas coal black. She had a twinkle in
OL,11,Fher eyes and was always bubbly.
OL,13,F"I fair miss her, so I do."
OL,15,FMs Wilson said it has been "hell"
OL,16,Fknowing her daughter's killer has not
OL,17,Fbeen brought to justice.
OL,19,F"I'm even looking myself at people
OL,20,Fwalking by me," she said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@dO]qD@AOUuD@AOUuD@[O]wD@\OUwD@
OL,26,AaO]{D@AOU|D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774832614
OL,3,C'You never heal' ` families still
OL,4,Cgrieving decades after Glasgow murders
OL,6,F"I'm really hurt. I've lost my
OL,7,Fdaughter in these circumstances, and I
OL,8,Fjust wish to God that that bandit was
OL,9,Fput away for a long time."
OL,11,FMs McCash finally saw her sister's
OL,12,Fmurderer convicted after a wait of two
OL,13,Fdecades.
OL,15,FShe had some words of advice for all
OL,16,Fthe families still waiting for justice
OL,17,Fof their own.
OL,19,F"Keep your hope, don't give up," she
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@ZO]{D@AOU{D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774832614
OL,3,C'You never heal' ` families still
OL,4,Cgrieving decades after Glasgow murders
OL,6,F"You might wait 10 or 50 years, but as
OL,7,Flong as your family know that this
OL,8,Fcould happen one day.
OL,10,F"We honestly gave up hope thinking
OL,11,Fthat this would never happen.
OL,13,F"He wasn't in the system and then he
OL,14,Fgot caught with a stupid crime.
OL,16,F"The pain won't go away but talk about
OL,17,Fyour loved person.
OL,19,F"Look at pictures and look at parties.
OL,20,FIf you don't talk, you hurt harder."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@AOUxD@AOU{D@AOU|D@dO]
