OL,3,C'You never heal' ` families still
OL,4,Cgrieving decades after Glasgow murders
OL,6,FThe Beware Book podcast takes its name
OL,7,Ffrom a journal which was used by women
OL,8,Finvolved in prostitution to warn each
OL,9,Fother about potentially dangerous or
OL,10,Fsuspicious clients.
OL,12,FThe podcast is being released
OL,13,Ffollowing the conviction of Iain
OL,14,FPacker, who was brought to justice
OL,15,Falmost two decades after murdering
OL,16,FEmma Caldwell in 2005.
OL,18,FThe relatives of those who were killed
OL,19,Fsay they have not been contacted by
OL,20,FPolice Scotland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
