OL,3,C'You never heal' ` families still
OL,4,Cgrieving decades after Glasgow murders
OL,6,FAs well as Ms Gallagher, the deaths of
OL,7,FKaren McGregor, Leona McGovern and
OL,8,FDiane McInally have not been solved.
OL,10,FA Police Scotland spokesperson said:
OL,11,F"All unresolved and unsolved homicides
OL,12,Fremain under review which means
OL,13,Fthey're never closed.
OL,15,F"When new information, new evidence,
OL,16,Fcomes to light, we do act upon it."
